title: Etka 7.4 / AU.SE.SK.VW (2013)
description:
Etka 7.4 / AU.SE.SK.VW 2013



Audi/volkswagen/seat/Skoda


Finally released the newest version of etka 7.4
WORKS ONLY on the 32bit version.


- The best part of this new 7.4 version is that no data needed to be extracted in order to update. 
-Update can be run by pressing the etka update manager on desktop.

Quick Installation guide:

1. Run setup (select c:/ or whatever)
2. serial key to activate (included)
3. After finished installed, make sure to install the hardlock and the emulator. 
4. Install the crack included in the folder (Crack by Voliacom)

note!

If problem finding the hardlock use the one in the folder..
